OL,3,CSon calls for assisted dying law
OL,4,Cchange after father left 'beaten husk
OL,5,Cof a man'
OL,7,FMr Malone said his father "was a big,
OL,8,Fstrong man", but was left "a beaten
OL,9,Fhusk of a man, rolling around in a
OL,10,Fhospital bed without any dignity"
OL,11,Fbefore he died.
OL,13,FHe added that the final four weeks of
OL,14,Fhis father's life were "like something
OL,15,Fout of a horror film".
OL,17,FIt comes as a new bill to legalise
OL,18,Fassisted dying in England and Wales
OL,19,Fwas formally introduced in the House
OL,20,Fof Commons on Wednesday 16 October.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
