OL,3,CSon calls for assisted dying law
OL,4,Cchange after father left 'beaten husk
OL,5,Cof a man'
OL,7,FThe debate and first vote on the bill
OL,8,Fare not expected to take place until
OL,9,Fthe end of November, but it will be
OL,10,Fthe first time the issue has been
OL,11,Fvoted on in the Commons in almost a
OL,12,Fdecade.
OL,14,FMr Malone said: "We should have been
OL,15,Fable to help him. If he was a farm
OL,16,Fanimal we would've been prosecuted,
OL,17,Fand rightly so for causing unnecessary
OL,18,Fsuffering, but he wasn't a farm animal
OL,19,Fhe was a man.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
