OL,3,CSon calls for assisted dying law
OL,4,Cchange after father left 'beaten husk
OL,5,Cof a man'
OL,7,F"The memory of those last four weeks
OL,8,Fis just horrendous, and we could've
OL,9,Fstopped that.
OL,11,F"If I'd had any courage, I could have
OL,12,Fput his pillow over his face and leant
OL,13,Fon it, and I often think now that
OL,14,Fthat's what I should've done."
OL,16,FUltimately, Mr Malone's father died
OL,17,Ffrom natural causes.
OL,19,FExplained: The Assisted Dying Bill and
OL,20,Fwhy some say it's controversial
