OL,3,CSon calls for assisted dying law
OL,4,Cchange after father left 'beaten husk
OL,5,Cof a man'
OL,7,FMr Malone said in 2010, his brother
OL,8,FMichael took his own life at home
OL,9,Fafter being diagnosed with the same
OL,10,Fincurable cancer as their father.
OL,12,FHe said his brother was determined to
OL,13,Favoid the extremely painful death
OL,14,Ftheir father had endured and wanted
OL,15,Fhis wife Vicky to be with him as he
OL,16,Fdied.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
