OL,3,CSon calls for assisted dying law
OL,4,Cchange after father left 'beaten husk
OL,5,Cof a man'
OL,7,FShe faced a six month police
OL,8,Finvestigation and was found to have
OL,9,Fdone nothing wrong, but Mr Malone said
OL,10,Fit added to the trauma of her
OL,11,Fexperience.
OL,13,F"On top of the trauma of his death, to
OL,14,Fbe subjected to that sort of
OL,15,Fbehaviour, even though the police were
OL,16,Fas sympathetic as they possibly could
OL,17,Fbe, added torment to trauma in a way
OL,18,Fthat was really unconscionable," he
OL,19,Fsaid.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
