OL,3,CSon calls for assisted dying law
OL,4,Cchange after father left 'beaten husk
OL,5,Cof a man'
OL,7,FLast year, Mr Malone's sister, Trudi,
OL,8,Falso chose to end her own life aged
OL,9,F71, after being diagnosed with Motor
OL,10,FNeurone Disease.
OL,12,FShe travelled to Switzerland where
OL,13,Fassisted suicide is legal, but Mr
OL,14,FMalone told ITV News West Country "she
OL,15,Fshould have been able to die at home".
OL,17,F"She should have been in her own bed,
OL,18,Fwith her family around her and the
OL,19,Fdogs on the bed, and maybe somebody
OL,20,Feven to hold her hand," he said.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
