OL,7,FKim Leadbeater, the Labour MP who
OL,8,Fintroduced the assisted dying bill to
OL,9,FParliament, said the legislation is
OL,10,F"about people who are terminally ill"
OL,11,Fwhen asked about the concerns disabled
OL,12,Fpeople have about the risks of
OL,13,Flegalising assisted dying.
